name: To Release is To Resolve
text: Pizza is fine, staff are okay. I've used the online ordering multiple times no problem.

name: robert drain
text: Needs more employees

name: Chris Brooks
text: I've slowly watched the decline of this location. Great pizza but this store has no staff. I've ordered via the app and the pizza is never ready when I arrive. There's usually a line of people waiting due to the lack of staff here. Thankfully there are other locations nearby.

name: Roy Minjarez
text: I think papa Murphy is one of the best pizza out there. They always put plenty of toppings and there sauce is great. Never been disappointed in their flavors.

name: pmckinn1
text: Just came back from vacation to watch the continued decline of this location. No salads or other add ons in cooler, unfriendly staff, and $10 Tues upgrade increased to $16.95, other stores $3 only, sad to see the complete decline of what useto be the best store in East metro area.

name: newtheis
text: My first visit, the pizza was delicious and the service was good. My second time was a waste. I walked in, but apparently had no salads.  Then I ordered a pizza they were advertising on their monitor and they would not honor the offer.  I left empty handed

name: Joseph halpin
text: Always prepared to our order. Fast service.

name: Joni Beechley
text: Went there,  ordered 2 pizzas. They said they had a power outage earlier in the day so their credit card machine was acting up. After waiting for 30 minutes, after my pizzas were made, they announced they were only accepting cash.  Due to I …More

name: Bradley Challis
text: LOVE the delite pizza! Great service - in and out in no time.  Terrific Value.  Glad to have a Papa Murphy's so close!

name: Kelsey Middlebrook
text: I love Papa Murphy’s pizza but this location is no good. I’ve been twice and both times the messed up my order

name: Brandon Roding
text: The store is almost always staffed with attentive, courteous folks, but sometimes volume in the store can get crazy.  One tip: Absent a line, it's faster to visit the location, order, pay and receive pizza than it is to place an order on the app (bundling in their mandatory 30-minute gap between order and pickup).

name: David Johnson
text: As long as you don't mind cooking the pizza at home this is actually really good pizza for a good price. Get their emails for discounts.

name: Denise Renee
text: Bad service  went to pick up a pizza that we ordered over the phone. Our order was wrong and we got 2 five dollar salads that were old. I asked if they were made fresh the supervisor said no

name: Lucas Jackson
text: Zero stars. Location doesn't show-up online for ordering and no one answers the phone. Total Joke

name: Mark Challis
text: Terrific Value, fresh ingredients,  fast and friendly service.  Live the delite pizzas!!

name: Michael Nelson
text: Understaffed - just picked up an order i made at 5:06.  Showed up with a huge line and just one poor kid working alone.  When they say "10-15 minutes" on the phone, it should be that, not 35 minutes later.  Seems like management must be …More

name: john mcmahon
text: Real good and good value

name: Mathieu Leboeuf
text: We love their pizza ! Super easy to cook !

name: Jerry Adams
text: Understand working a black girl like she was a dog.

name: Perry Friedentag
text: New NYXL pizza just ok you get what you pay for...$8

name: Aaron Jones
text: It's ok. The drawback is watching them make pizza. It's like watching paint dry. Order ahead.

name: PM How 2
text: Dumb  people who can't get one order right.

name: Angelique Fernlund
text: Location Closed

name: Bailey Hagen
text: Awesome pizza

name: Cecilia Wetzbarger
text: This location is good and gets a lot of business.

name: Michael Freitas
text: The manager is unprofessional and was very rude to me when I went to pick up my phone-in order. I am never going to return to this Papa Murphy's again.

name: George Valdez
text: Could be more economical pricing.

name: Gene Galushko
text: Would not honor a special.  Cannot think outside the box and was wrong about modifying items.  Order online, DO NOT call in.  Terrible service!

name: Stephanie Osborn
text: Never had a wait .

name: Jeff Orzel
text: Window sign says open till 9, told was closed at 8:10, gentleman was very rude even though door was unlocked.
